        <div class="main review-item" id="1012926">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1035287/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u1035287-1.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1035287/" class="name">草莓</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2005-11-30" class="main-meta">2005-11-30 17:09:32</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1012926/">这是一本很有价值的中国哲学笔记</a></h2>

